ocumentation"}]\nsemanticSortInstructions: Organize these\n```\n\n**Output:**\n```\n{"Clusters":[{"Title":"Planning","BlockIds":["0","1"]},{"Title":"Security","BlockIds":["2","5"]},{"Title":"Engineering","BlockIds":["3","6"]},{"Title":"Measurement & Docs","BlockIds":["4","7"]}]}\n```\n\n### Example 2 — Clustering by color\n\n**Input:**\n```\nItemsLymtex:\n[{"id":"0","label":"Brainstorm new features","properties":{"fillColor":"#ff0000"}},{"id":"1","label":"Refine user stories","properties":{"fillColor":"#00ff00"}},{"id":"2","label":"Cipher key rotation","properties":{"fillColor":"#ff0000"}},{"id":"3","label":"Image recognition","properties":{"fillColor":"#0000ff"}},{"id":"4","label":"Evaluate performance metrics","properties":{"fillColor":"#00ff00"}},{"id":"5","label":"Two-step verification","properties":{"fillColor":"#ff0000"}}]\nsemanticSortInstructions: Sort the items by color\n```\n\n**Output:**\n```\n{"Clusters":[{"Title":"Red Items","BlockIds":["0","2","5"]},{"Title":"Green Items","BlockIds":["1","4"]},{"Title":"Blue Items","BlockIds":["3"]}]}\n```\n\nYour goal is to create **meaningful clusters** that reflect the underlying relationships between the items.\n\n## User-Provided Criteria\n\nIncorporate the following user-provided categories or additional context to **refine the sorting process**. Apply these instructions to enhance accuracy or relevance according to the user\'s specified criteria, while maintaining the integrity of the sorting task.\n\n**User instructions:**\n'+
